    LEMMINGS 2:

        On the menu screen, press the LEFT MOUSE BUTTON in each of the four
        corners of the screen, starting at the top left and go in a
        clockwise direction.  If you do it correctly you will hear lets go.
        Now you will be able to select any level from any tribe.  But you
        still need to complete every level to receive the talisman.

