    PETER BEARDSLEY'S INTERNATIONAL SOCCER:

        Continual tapping of the fire button while in possession of the ball
        prevents any other players from tackling.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p13
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    PGA TOUR GOLF:

        Before you tee off on the first hole click the button for the
        tournament statistics.  Look through all of these and then play the
        game as usual and you'll find that your opponents have dropped quite
        a few shots.  Do this on each hole, and by the end of the game the
        computer players will be quite a way behind you.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p14
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    PHANTASIA III:

        When you go to deposit some gold and are asked how much type
        "9999999".  This will be turned into a deposit of 27009.  Do not
        deposit any more or your account will be nothing.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p15
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *PHARAOHS CURSE:

        Type "SPHINX" to start on level 2 or type "RAIDER" for level 3.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p16
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *PHOTON STORM: (Keith Krellwitz)

        Pause the game and type "YOUR-MIND-IS-MY-ASHTRAY" for invincibility.
        Were the '-' (minus signs) are on the main keyboard.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p17
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *PINBALL FANTASIES: (Keith Krellwitz)

        On any table while the table is scolling up and down type any of
        the following:

        "DIGITAL ILLUSIONS"_______________________Ball can't be lost.
        "FAIR PLAY"_________________Resets eveything back to default.
        "EARTHQUAKE"_______________________________Disables the tilt.
        "EXTRA BALLS"____________________Five balls instead of three.
        "VACUUM CLEANER"______________________Clears the high scores.
        "THE SILENTS"_______________________Message from the silents.
        "HIGHLANDER"_________________________________________Message.
        "TECH STUFF"_________________________________Technical stuff.
        "ULF"______________________________________Message about ulf.
        "OLOF"____________________________________Message about olof.
        "MARKUS"________________________________Message about markus.
        "ANDREAS"______________________________Message about andreas.
        "BARRY"__________________________________Message about barry.
        "FREDRIK"______________________________Message about fredrik.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p18
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    PINBALL MAGIC:

        When the exit to the next level opens, you can press 'F4' to go to
        the next level.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p19
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    PIPELINE:

        The level codes are "FOLD", "EYES", "EGGS", "TEAR", "PEAS", "DUCT",
        AND "PODS".

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p20
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    PIPEMANIA:

        The level codes are:

            04-"GRIP"       12-"DUCK"       20-"BLOB"       28-"WILD"
            08-"TICK"       16-"OOZE"       24-"BALL"

        For a 4000 point bonus, you need to get the flooze to cross itself
        five times.  But remember not to get too cocky, and wait until the
        end of the pipe to do this.  There is also a secret bonus of 50,000
        points if you completely fill the screen with pipes.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p21
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    PIRATES:

        When fighting against unbelievable odds dont panic.  Choose the long
        sword.  Keep using the slash-high attack to cause the most dammage.
        You may get down to only one man left,  but you can still defeat the
        enemy captain.  After you win, select send a prize crew so you will
        have enough people to sail your ship.

        Don't attack a nation your home country is allied with, it will
        upset both of them.

        Don't wed till you've got all your promotions, your oppurtunities
        will be much better.  Make conversation with all the governors
        daughters, however, they might gather important information for
        you from the governors mansion.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p22
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *PITFIGHTER:

        Start the game and type "LOBSTERS", use the numeric key pad '1',
        '2', and '3') to advance to the corresponding level.  Then try these
        keys:

                    'L'______________For elimination round.
                    'G'__________________ For grudge match.
                    'C'______ For final championship round.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p23
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    PLAGUE, THE:

        First make your score end in a three (by shooting the bubbles).
        Then hit 'P' to pause the game, then hit 'ESC', then click {No}
        when asked if you want to play again. This takes you to the title
        screen with drooling barbarian.  Now type the following:
        "KOM JE ILLEGAAL DOOR DE PLAAG DAN GRIJPT DE JUNGLE COMMAND JE IN
        DE KRAGG" (space in between each word), then hit Return.  Border
        should turn green.  Hit fire button to return to game and you will
        have infinite lives.  You must do this on Level 1 before killed for
        the first time.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p24
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *PLATOON:

        On the title screen, type "HAMBURGER".  The word {Cheat} will appear
        below the credits press your joystck button, then 'F5' when the
        jungle screen comes up.  During play press any of the following
        keys:

                'F1'_____________Starts you where you currently are.
                'F2'___________Starts you at location of explosives.
                'F3'__Starts you at the bridges you need to blow up.
                'F4'______Starts you at the village (hidden tunnel).
                     (Cheat doesn't work any further than this)

        If you type "-HILL" (where the hyphen is the minus on the keypad)
        after you have typed "HAMBURGER".  When the credit screen re-appears
        the words {MEGA CHEAT} will appear when the credits scroll.
        

                 'F2'____________________________Start a TNT.
                 'F3'____________________Start at the bridge.
                 'F4'___________________Start at the village. 
                 'F5'_______________immunity from everything.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p25
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    PLAYER MANAGER:

        1.  Buy a few young, cheap players and keep them in the squad for a
            whole season. Next year, their price will have increased and you
            should have no trouble selling them for a huge profit. 

        2.  Only buy players with very high agility ratings, as this effects
            all their other attributes. If agility is high (about 200),
            expect the player to become an excellent footballer, given a
            season or two. 

        3.  Remove 8 or 9 players from your team, then after 2 or 3 big
            defeats you will receive sponsorship.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p26
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *POD (PD): (Keith Krellwitz)

        On the title screen, type "BIGCOUNTRY" and then a level number.
    
        EXAMPLE: Type "BIGCOUNTRY45", then press 'F1' (1 player) or 'F2'
        (2 players).  You will start on level 45.
 
     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p27
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *POING (PD):

        On the title screen, hold the 'LEFT SHIFT' key and press '[' to
        enter the editor.  Also press 'R-AMIGA' and 'N' to go to workbench
        and 'R-AMIGA' and 'M' to get back to the game.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p28
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    POOL OF RADIANCE:

        Once you find any item you  can make as many copies of it as you
        want.

        1. Create a dummy character.

        2. Load a saved game and transfer all the good items to the dummy.

        3. Remove the dummy character from the party.

        4. Load the dummy character back in.

        5. Transfer the items to other members.

        6. Drop the dummy character from the party.

        7. Repeat steps 4-6 as many times as needed.

        This also works for Curse of the Azure Bonds and Champions of Krynn.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node p29
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "P"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

