        With 1 being the team on the left, 2 the middle team, and 3 the team
        on the right.  Keep the key pressed down and move the pointer under
        the door and click the LEFT BUTTON four times, then the RIGHT BUTTON
        four times.  The border should flash to let you know if it worked.

        While being attacked, press 'ESC' key repeatedly.  This will reduce
        attacker's score, inflicting less damage on your soldiers.

