    STARFLIGHT:

        In the trade depot at the space station, buy 1000 units of endurium.
        Then sell it all back for an additional 20,000 MU'S.  If you only
        sell back 990 the you will get 2,714,000 MU'S.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node s71
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "S"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    STARGLIDER:

        Slow down the ship completely and press 'F1' for fixed sights.
        Press the 'BACKSPACE' to pause the game.  Now type "JS ARG S" and
        hit return (twice).  This will give infinite life, fuel, and
        shields.  It may be JS(Space)ARG(Backspace)S(Backspace)(Return).
        Now use any of the following keys:

                    'P'......................Restock missiles.
                    'E'......................Reboots the disk.
                    'N'.................Gives you 5000 points.
                    'M'..................Stops enemy aircraft.
                    'Z'..................Secret object viewer.

        To enter the secret object viewer, press 'z'.  Then press 'p' to
        pause.  Select '[', and ']' and manipulate objects.  You can use
        all keys but 'q' and 'ESC'.  Use the mouse to change point of view,
        or magnification with right mouse button.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node s72
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "S"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *STARGLIDER II:

        1st:    Slow down the ship completely and press 'F' for fixed
                sights.  Press the 'BACKSPACE' key to pause the game.

        2nd:    Type "WERE ON A MISSION FROM GOD" and press '1'.  This
                should make you invincible.  Press 'K' to receive all
                weapons.

        WHERE TO GET WHAT AND HOW: 
 
            BOUNCING BOMBS:
                Castron Depot, use on projector bases only. 
 
            MISSILES:
                Millway Depots, use on walkers, stompers, etc... 
 
            CUBOIDS:
                Use a lot of energy, given to you by Prof Taymar. 
 
            NEUTRON BOMB:
                Use on space station only. 
 
            CASK OF VISTAN VINE:
                Get from pirates, or trade a boink at the Castron Depot. 
 
            CLUSTER OF NODULES:
                On beautiful downtown Dante. 
 
            EGRON MINI-ROCKET:
                Surface of Aldos or Q-beta. 
 
            CASE OF NUKE FUEL:
                Aldos surface. 
 
            ASTEROID:
                Between Apogee and Millway, in the asteroid belt. 
 
            FLAT DIAMOND:
                Capture a mech whale, take it to the Questa Depot, and
                trade it in for a flat diamond. 
 
            LUMP OF MINERAL ROCK:
                Q-beta surface. 
 
            CRATE OF CASTROBARS:
                Go to Enos and grab a tree, trade it in at the Castron
                Depot ("LOOKEVERYBODY!  TOOTHPICKS!!!"). 
 
            PROFESSOR TAYMAR:
                After getting all of the above ingredients, go to broadway.
                Make sure you have a crate of castrobars in the hold. 

            Cruise the surface and tractor beam the first emma 2 you see.
            Bring it aboard.  Taymar is inside.  He will install the cuboid
            launcher and agree to go to apogee.  Take him to the Apogee
            Depot.  When the neutron bomb is built, take it to Q-beta's
            false moon.  If all 6 projector bases have been rebuilt, drop by
            one and blow it up.  You will see the space station, surrounded
            by mini-sentinels.  Take a couple out with missiles.  Move
            toward the station, and when you're directly over it, drop the
            bomb.  A massive explosion follows, and you win the game!!!

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node s73
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "S"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

