        On the title screen when the title appears or on the options screen
        type "TODAZ IS HER BIRTHDAZ" if your using an American amiga or type
        "TODAY IS HER BIRTHDAY" if the Y and Z keys are switched:  the Y be
        next to the X key.  Now use the following keys during play:
        
