    *VOLFIED: (Keith Krellwitz)

        Get a score of exactly 10 points and press 'ESC' or the key right
        under 'ESC'.  Now go to the difficulty setting and scroll through
        the options.  You will notice a new option (CHEAT).  You can now
        start on any level with infinite lives.  Your shields will also
        last longer and the little enemies can't kill you when they run
        into your path.

