@endnode
@node w02
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "W"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    WALKER:

        As soon as you appear on level two (don't move the walker at all),
        type "EAT LEAD MUDDY FUNSTER".

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node w03
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "W"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *WAR IN THE GULF:

        On the filing screen, pop up a file and type in "Let me cheat!".
        Type it exactly as shown (Do not press return).  Now click on the
        reset button, and go into the game.  You can now choose to go to any
        of the squares on the map.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node w04
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "W"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    WARHAWK:

        After loading, press 'F3'.  When the game start a blue blob appears
        on the screen.  Pick it up and you will get infinite power.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node w05
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "W"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------

    WARHEAD:

        The very first time you attack the berserker, hit him with
        everything you have, including the MDC.  He will then keep following
        you.  When Solbase says to take him anywhere, go to CH010 and he
        will get sucked into a black hole.

        To evade missiles, your best bet is to fly away backwards in front
        of them at a range of about 3000 m.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node w06
             @{" GO BACK ONE PAGE        " Link "W"}  @{"  BACK TO THE ALPHABET   " Link "Index"}

