        On the title screen type one of the following:

                "THE PERFECT KISS"_________Infinite ammunition.
                "SOULPSYCHEDELICIDE"__________Infinite extends.

        Or while playing type "ITS NOT ALL WALKING", When you restart the
        game you can skip to the last level you completed.  You can only use
        one.

     -----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
